        "URI": "-",
        "DOI": "-",
        "Extended description": "Calculates daily average soil temperature at the center of each soil layer using a damping-depth approach. The model uses layer depths, bulk density, soil water content, surface temperature and an annual mean temperature to compute a damping depth and update soil layer temperatures and daily temperature change rates.",
