        "description": "Process the algorithm and update SoilTempArray and rSoilTempArrayRate for each soil layer using damping depth and surface temperature.",
        "firstLine": "if(iDoInitialize.getValue())",
        "lastLine": "SoilTempArray.setArrayValue(i, SoilTempArray.getValue()[i] + rSoilTempArrayRate.getValue()[i], this);"
    },
